'''Viptiel''' was a [[Plant/Legends|plant]] native to [[Nal Hutta/Legends|Nal Hutta]]. It was known for its therapeutic properties to the [[X'Ting]] for its hormone-balancing effects during that [[Species/Legends|species]]' transition from one gender to the other; however, very few could afford it. [[Vippit]]s also used viptiel as a medicinal supplement, especially during their mating periods.

